    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, a mechanical masterpiece featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis remains taut, riding on refreshed bushings and OEM dampers. All VIN tags are present, and the finish retains its deep luster. A turn-key specimen for the purist who demands peak performance and structural integrity.",
